      <description><![CDATA[
<b>New:</b>
<ul>
<li>You can now drag to make the popover taller or shorter, and the popover is slightly wider out of the box.</li>
</ul>
<b>Improved:</b>
<ul>
<li>Closing the settings window now stops the live preview from continuously updating, reducing battery and CPU use.</li>
</ul>
<b>Fixes:</b>
<ul>
<li>Quitting the app now properly removes the menu bar icon and popover, preventing a leftover icon from appearing.</li>
</ul>
      ]]></description>
